Leader Development Corp said ithas purchased 300,000 shares of convertible preferred stock in&lt;Petrosurance Inc> for 1,500,000 dlrs in cash and real estate.    Petrosurance specializes in property and casualty insurancefor the oil industry.    Leader said the stock is convertible into a Petrosurancecommon. Leader said it already owns 12.5 pct of Petrorusranceand conversion would give it about 45.0 pct.    The company said Petrosurance will use the sale proceeds tosupport growth and improve the structure of its reinsurancetreaties to retain a larger part of premiums written. Reuter&#3;